---------

git import-dsc &lt;package&gt;.dsc

Updating
--------

git import-orig -u &lt;version&gt; &lt;source&gt;.tar.gz

Releasing
---------

git dch --release
git dch --snapshot
git dch --snapshot --auto

Building
--------

git buildpackage --git-ignore-new
git buildpackage --git-tag

Creating
--------

$ mkdir package-0.1
$ cd package-0.1
$ git init

$ git import-orig -u 0.1 ../package-0.1.tar.gz
$ dh_make</pre></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="footer">Powered by <a href="http://www.sinatrarb.com/">Sinatra</a>,
